\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/how-event-aggregator-is-solving-problems-for-stanford-law/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 29 Jan 2018 18:30:24 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Showcase\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"campus\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"college\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"education\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"facilities management\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/?p=1426762\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:687:\"<p>About Stanford Law Stanford Law School is a prominent university widely regarded for its world-class lectures. They offer students a rich campus life filled with extra-curricular activities, organizations, and events. Coordinating this mass of events and lectures across countless departments and student groups can be a logistical nightmare. Stanford Law needed an intuitive way to&#8230;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/how-event-aggregator-is-solving-problems-for-stanford-law/\">How Event Aggregator is solving problems for Stanford Law</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"enclosure\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:84:\"http://theeventscalendar.com/content/uploads/2018/01/stanford-walkthrough-comped.mp4\";s:6:\"length\";s:3:\"194\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"video/mp4\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Hillary Schlaht\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4518:\"<h2>About Stanford Law</h2>\n<p>Stanford Law School is a prominent university widely regarded for its world-class lectures. They offer students a rich campus life filled with extra-curricular activities, organizations, and events.</p>\n<p>Coordinating this mass of events and lectures across countless departments and student groups can be a logistical nightmare. Stanford Law needed an intuitive way to loop their facilities team into each event that was being uploaded to their calendar to ensure they had the capacity to host each event. When they came to us to rebuild their site, we used <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/\">The Events Calendar</a> suite of plugins to build a system that they could use to easily and effectively coordinate all their campus events.</p>\n<h2>Event Aggregator to the rescue</h2>\n<p>The Stanford Law facilities team is responsible for the execution of all events that occur on campus. By using the <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/product/event-aggregator/\">Event Aggregator</a> service, they can import a comprehensive list of every university event to their own calendar to use for preparation and planning. Every event that is added to the Stanford Law events calendar is sent as a draft to the facilities departments private calendar for review using the Event Aggregator service.</p>\n<p>The facilities team will then review the event to determine whether it is viable. They will check if the location requested for the event is available at that time and what equipment will be needed (e.g. tables &amp; chairs).</p>\n<p>If the event is approved, they publish it on their own, internal calendar. From there, they can build it into their schedule and assign cleaning, maintenance, A/V technicians, and other necessary staff to make sure the event meets Stanford Law standards.</p>\n<h2>What this means for Stanford Law</h2>\n<p>Stanford Law hosts an incredible range of groups who each want to host multiple events in connection with the university. Allowing people to upload their own events to the calendar saves the administration team tons of work, and offers a more colorful, rich and diverse calendar for the patrons of the university.</p>\n<p>Anyone can add their events to the calendar using <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/product/wordpress-community-events/\">Community Events</a>. This includes a university administrator announcing a speech from the Dean or even a student arranging a movie night in their dorm.</p>\n<p>Admins can create their events from the back-end using <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/product/wordpress-events-calendar-pro/\">The Events Calendar PRO</a> and student groups and other associations can submit their events for approval by the Student Activities board using Community Events.</p>\n<p>Ultimately, the use of Community Events across campus helps Stanford Law to host a master calendar with more events than any single department or group could manage.</p>\n<p>Since the university has such a diverse community of professors, students, admins, donors, and alumni, the university has installed <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/product/wordpress-events-filterbar/\">Filter Bar</a> to help their website users quickly and easily narrow down their search to events that are relevant to them.</p>\n<p>Our suite of events management plugins provides Stanford Law with the foundation for an entirely customized event-planning process that allows them to host hundreds of events without overreaching their capabilities or compromising their high standards.</p>\n<p>Check out their unique implementation and customization in the screencast below!</p>\n<div style=\"width: 980px;\" class=\"wp-video\"><!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement(\'video\');</script><![endif]-->\n<video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-1426762-1\" width=\"980\" height=\"706\" loop=\"1\" autoplay=\"1\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video/mp4\" src=\"http://theeventscalendar.com/content/uploads/2018/01/stanford-walkthrough-comped.mp4?_=1\" /><a href=\"http://theeventscalendar.com/content/uploads/2018/01/stanford-walkthrough-comped.mp4\">http://theeventscalendar.com/content/uploads/2018/01/stanford-walkthrough-comped.mp4</a></video></div>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/how-event-aggregator-is-solving-problems-for-stanford-law/\">How Event Aggregator is solving problems for Stanford Law</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"The Events Calendar 4.6.10.1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0: